data.description: Welcome Home to 311 Rail Spike Road located in Speers Crossing Subdivision! This house has it all!! This home features 4 really spacious bedrooms and 3 full bathrooms. An oversized kitchen with huge island with granite countertops, stainless appliances, and storage galore are just a few of the amazing features this home has to offer! Private backyard with large screened in porch makes for perfect Mississippi Fall evenings for cooking outback! This one won't last long!! Call you realtor today for your showing!
